{"tid":2456764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"龍門冰室/瓏門冰室  銅鑼灣分店  做埋今日 應該無得再做喇  日如無意外 會有執達理嚟到收舖","createTime":"2021-03-22T07:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T13:46:57.000Z","uid":179775,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4606ef2d610c467ba00f446a95a5bdb1545926","tid":2456764,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:21:17.000Z","msg":"呢兩個星期<br />\n好多謝香港人嚟到瓏門支持我哋<br />\n但有樣嘢<br />\n我諗都係時候同大家講<br />\n銅鑼灣分店 <br />\n做埋今日 應該無得再做喇<br />\n聽日如無意外<br />\n會有執達理嚟到收舖<br />\n其實一直以來<br />\n銅鑼灣分店虧損比較嚴重<br />\n無奈之下 唯有忍痛結業<br />\n之後大家想支持瓏門啲<br />\n可能要過返海喇<br />\n雖然瓏門喺港島區 再無立足之地<br />\n但臨別之時<br />\n我亦衷心希望各位香港人能夠支持<br />\n港島區嘅黃店<br />\n喺香港營運一間餐廳絕非易事<br />\n喺依家呢個大環境下 仲難<br />\n餐廳真係好需要大家嘅支持<br />\n先可以繼續行到落去<br />\n於我而言 同行未必如敵國<br />\n瓏門出品嘅「暗然銷魂飯」<br />\n好老實講我覺得真係唔錯<br />\n但其實銅鑼灣 登龍街入面<br />\n有一間黃店嘅滑蛋叉燒飯都好好味<br />\n大家真心可以行入去試下"},{"pid":"69a2a4b9d50d148138b15e604fd0cdf6c43c99a1","tid":2456764,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf301485905c0a8c89d0f8db9878f5c26ad9da3","tid":2456764,"uid":164752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfe7c2473f4447164c335cecdac97c7f1f1d7a4","tid":2456764,"uid":313334,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:23:51.000Z","msg":"兒登吹到點救龍門幾好食都係照執柒<br />\n果然係一班冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"139ee76f80ab6c694b6b92f95e8a7f65c7650265","tid":2456764,"uid":12599,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"剩返三間, 唔該做好個水準佢<br />\n<br />\n淨係講政治野食難食係唔會有人返轉頭"},{"pid":"168ca0f920af5d6b91f95179209d3156884b7668","tid":2456764,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:24:47.000Z","msg":"比人全方位打<br />\n<br />\n唔執就奇啦<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵比藍絲笑"},{"pid":"eb45d39d5cc701dc092cf32497e1116184eac041","tid":2456764,"uid":179775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"139ee76f80ab6c694b6b92f95e8a7f65c7650265","tid":2456764,"uid":12599,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"剩返三間, 唔該做好個水準佢<br />\n<br />\n淨係講政治野食難食係唔會有人返轉頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"其實佢後期D野食唔差<br />\n<br />\n重要KEEP住大大份"},{"pid":"b5accdd218f8cbc3a32ab5f7b25414ff3483e263","tid":2456764,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"人地時代逆市買2間<br />\n<br />\n佢就執幾間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有心做咪問下蕭生點搞<br />\n<br />\n不過蕭生 <br />\n<br />\n生意佬d蔥油秘方 點煮法應該收收埋埋"},{"pid":"05137a6527ccd8d4b0fac1720094af0c3536e925","tid":2456764,"uid":291750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:36:23.000Z","msg":"各區都有告急"},{"pid":"73142f5decc099a77e47ed02ebfe79b76fe26bdc","tid":2456764,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"前兩日有去食<br />\n啲野食唔錯"},{"pid":"87c08fb037a76648bfd045800c2bc1ac5085d2ed","tid":2456764,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持龍門"},{"pid":"d4b354b36ec3957cba0985